{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"affacb2ef0","title":"关于停止内战一致抗日的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6db8e70318","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"affacb2ef0"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8f89dcf7ac","type":"paragraph","text":"关于停止内战一致抗日的谈话”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"affacb2ef0"},{"id":"c0c1359618","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月15日）苏维埃中央政府与人民红军军事委员会，现已发布命令：（一）一切红军部队停止对国民革命军之任何攻击行为：（二）仅在被攻击时，允许采取必需之自卫手段：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"affacb2ef0"},{"id":"a75d312a3a","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）凡属国民革命军，因其向我进攻而被我缴获之人员武器，在该军抗日时，一律送还，其愿当红军者听","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"affacb2ef0"},{"id":"b2e12e71f3","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）如国民革命军向抗日阵地转移时，制止任何妨碍举动，并须给以一切可能之援助。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"affacb2ef0"},{"id":"11ddcb99d7","type":"paragraph","text":"吾人已决定再行息切申请一切国民革命军部队与南京政府，与吾人停战携手抗日。该项申请书已在草拟中。目前察普绥三省形势，已属危急方状。吾人极愿与南京政府合作，以达援绥抗日救亡图存之目的。如南京政府诚能顾念国难停止内战出兵抗日，苏维埃愿以全力援助，并愿以全国之红军主力为先锋，与日寇决一死战。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"affacb2ef0"},{"id":"80f95de3b1","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东以苏维埃中央政府主席名义通过苏维埃新闻社发表的谈话。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"affacb2ef0"}],"page":{"id":"cdf6e1151f","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"affacb2ef0","start":231,"end":231}}}},"__N_SSG":true}